commit.message:
patdiff-git-wrapper: Use /usr/bin/env bash instead of /bin/bash

/bin/bash doesn't exist on some systems, such as on NixOS.  Instead,
use whatever bash is in PATH.

Signed-off-by: Aaron L. Zeng <me@bcc32.com>
